Plot:

Thammar Boyfriend' is a feel-good comedy directed by Anindya Ghosh. The story revolves around a wealthy but lonely woman Nandini played by Sabitri Chatterjee, who decides to tie the knot again and found a young and handsome bridegroom in Abir's Partho! 'Thammar Boyfriend' is a rollercoaster ride that goes on to answer several questions, like who Partho really is and why did he agree to get hitched with Nandini. The film also features Arunima Ghosh, Biswajit Chakraborty and others
